    "Assessment of risk of biases using the PROBAST tool for generative AI model studies included in the meta-analysis (N = 54).",
    "The participants and the outcome determination were predominantly at low risk of bias, but there was a high risk of bias for analysis (83%) and the overall evaluation (83%).",
